<plot>Fabio Bonetti is married with Livia since almost 20 years. One day a private eye investigating on their neighbors, the Vitali family, by an error starts filming and recording Livia's life. When Fabio gets the films he discovers his family life is far from being tedious and flat. Livia is unfaithful, and their daughter Veronica is drug addicted. He is also under the menace of a terrible illness. Maybe Fabio will start considering a new way of life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?268174</url></doc>
